compensation in view of the centralized knight.[%csl Yc3,Yg4]} 22. Ne3 Ra7 $5
23. Bb3 Qxc3 24. Nd5 Qc8 25. Nb6 Qd8 26. Nxd7 Qxd7 27. Bd5 g6 $11 {Hracek,Z 
