Qe7 22. Be3 Bg7 {the knight is more of a source of worries.}) 20... Bh6 {A
logical move, preparing the exchange of the potentially "bad" bishop, which,
however, supposes some risks.} (20... h5 {looks premature.} 21. Qf3 Ne6 (21...
b4 22. cxb4 Ne6 23. Bb3 Ng5 24. Qe2 Nxe4 25. Nd5 $16) 22. Nd5 Bxd5 23. Rxd5 (
